&gt; Thoughts?</span >

I say do it.  You've interacted on the list and submitted a bug report against the spec, which has an active editor who will take care of it.  It seems clear that the right solution is to fix the spec to match browsers here, and we should adjust ourselves to be in line with that.</div>
    </div>
    


